README.md
Boost.Actor

Boost.Actor is a Boost-version of CAF, the C++ Actor Framework . It features lightweight & fast actor implementations, pattern matching for messages, network transparent messaging, and more.
Get the Sources

    git clone https://github.com/Neverlord/boost.actor.git
    cd boost.actor

First Steps

    ./configure
    make
    make install [as root, optional]

It is recommended to run the unit tests as well.

    make test

Please submit a bug report that includes (a) your compiler version, (b) your OS, and (c) the content of the file build/Testing/Temporary/LastTest.log if an error occurs.
Dependencies

    CMake
    Boost
    Pthread (until C++11 compilers support the new thread_local keyword)

Supported Compilers

    GCC >= 4.8
    Clang >= 3.4

Supported Operating Systems

    Linux
    Mac OS X
    Windows (beta)

